    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "but i don't want a new perspective. i don't want to look at the view. i'm just so tired of the weight of it all. looking down into that canyon... it doesn't feel scary. it actually feels quiet. like the only place where the noise finally stops. it feels like the only logical place to just... let go of the pack and stop fighting the wind.",
